{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-first-questions/task-11","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 11","description":"","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ovaj vežbaji nema zvuk. Dopuni razgovor koji je dole.</p>\n<p>Napišite ovu reč na pravo mesto:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mucho</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">llamo</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">igualmente</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">gracias</span></p>\n<p>Ima više reči nego mesta za popunjavanje. Nije potrebno da koristiš sve reči.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Razgovor između Rikarda i Daniela završava se sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Mucho gusto</span> (\"Hvala što sam te upoznao\") i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Igualmente</span> (\"I vi\").</p>\n<p>Ovo je uobičajen i pristojan način za verifikaciju identiteta na španskom.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-practice-first-questions","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-first-questions/task-11"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Ricardo: BLANK gusto.</p>\n<p>Daniel: BLANK.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Mucho","feedback":"<p>Ova reč znači \"veoma\" ili \"u množini\". To je prva reč u izrazu \"Nashukuru kukutana nawe\".</p>"},{"answer":"Igualmente","feedback":"<p>Ova reč znači \"tako\" ili \"njako\". To je uobičajen odgovor na izraz \"Drago mi je što sam te upoznao/upoznala.\"</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":null,"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-practice-first-questions","dashedName":"task-11","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":